PS1='\[\033[1;32m\]\u\[\033[0m\]@\[\033[1;32m\]\h\[\033[0m\] \W\[\033[0m\]\[\033[1;32m\]$(git_branch)\[\033[0m\] \[\033[1;32m\]❯\[\033[0m\] '
